steps.name: Navigate to PO For Stock screen
Verify the count of the PO Records in the PO grid before adding the PO record
Click on the Add Data Entry button
Verify whether the page is navigated to the Create PO For Stock or not
Select a Delivery To factory name
Select a Process for the selected Order Type
Enter the Quantity of the Fabric
Click on Save button in the Create PO For Stock screen
Verify whether the page is navigated to the PO For Stock or not
Verify the count of the PO Records in the PO grid after adding the PO record
Verify whether the added PO record is added to the grid
